item.title: Pi I need help Auto Cache downloading?
item.dc:creator: @deathe1000 deathe1000
item.description:
@deathe1000 wrote:

there are many places to get one, should be called cachedownloader.java you can find a download link for one at most webclient tutorials, look up justin’s webclient tutorial on runelocus or rune-server, (forgot which one) and he will have a download for you

also make sure you use drop box or file den for the download link you put into the cachedownloader, it needs to be direct download
